247
00:18:42.869 --> 00:18:45.963
¿Sedgewick?

248
00:18:47.674 --> 00:18:50.472
Exacto. Sedgewick.

249
00:18:51.645 --> 00:18:54.136
Ey! Se
-Sedgewick.

